title: The Sims 3 + crack (multilanguage)
description:
The Sims 3, fully working, cracks included in the 'crack' directory.

It is a multi language version so it should most of the time include the language you want it to be.

I tested it on a vista 64 bit computer, worked without problems.

There is 1 thing though, the installer might SEEM to hang at some systems, this is couse the installer might overload the memory(happend at a 2 gb RAM system of mine). Though, do NOT exit the installer, it will finish after a while. So just have a little patience and everything will just work ^^

So please, enjoy ^^


Greetings, Incapable91
